        <div class="intro">
            <p>The ALEX portal is a tool that uses virtual health educators to teach patients and caregivers about research studies. ALEX also has a search feature to help find research studies that might be of interest to you based on your health needs and interests.</p>
            <p style="margin-top:0px">ALEX can help you:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Explore what research studies are and how they can benefit you and your community.</li>
