                <li>Send an email to a research study staff member to get more information as a self-referral.</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top:0px">Whether you're facing a diagnosis or helping a loved one, the ALEX portal is a tool designed to help connect you with research studies that matter to you.  </p>
